== Introduction == <!--T:1-->

<!--T:2-->
The Stemfie Workbench is an [[External_workbenches|external workbench]] aimed at implementing a parametric set of parts for the [https://www.stemfie.org/ Stemfie project].

</translate>
[[File:Stemfie_WB.jpg|Stemfie Workbench set of parts|700px]]
<translate>

== Installing == <!--T:3-->

<!--T:4-->
The Stemfie workbench is not bundled with the default FreeCAD package, but can easily be installed via the [[Image:Std_AddonMgr.svg|24px]] [[Std_AddonMgr|Addon Manager]]. Invoke it from {{MenuCommand|Tools → [[Std_AddonMgr|Addons Manager]]}}. The Stemfie workbench code is [https://github.com/bilbaomakers/StemfieWB hosted and developed on github] and can also be installed manually by copying it into FreeCAD's {{FileName|MOD}} directory. 

== Getting started == <!--T:5-->

You just need to activate the command that creates the part you need, the workbench is separated on different toolbars, each one containing a category of elements.

== Tools == <!--T:6-->

=== Beams ===
* Beam - Straight - End Square Square
* Beam - Straight - End Round Round

=== Braces ===
* Brace - Straight - Standard - End Round Round

=== Connectors ===
* Connector - Through-Hole - Beam - Shaft - One-way
* Connector - Through-Hole - Beam - Shaft - Two-way 90°
* Connector - Through-Hole - Beam - Shaft - Two-way 180°
* Connector - Through-Hole - Beam - Shaft - Three-way
* Connector - Through-Hole - Beam - Shaft - Four-way

=== Plates ===
* Triangular plate
* Square plate
* Hexagonal plate

=== Shaft ===
* Shaft plain

== References == <!--T:6-->

<!--T:7-->
